title: I keep getting a "error" that I need to update Firefox to get into my bank but I have the latest update
content: How about fixing the damn thing. I used to have no problems when I logged into my bank (Chase) now when I try to log into my bank it says I need to up grade FireFox but I have the latest upgrade so what the hell do I need to do? It is your browser so fix the damn problem and make it work right.
